summary: This mod is my first and it's not finished, this is just a little teaser.
descriptionHtml:
DARK HARBOR

You can accesses to hidden harbor by Abandoned Prison the entrance should be at next to Prison interior entrance.

This mod is designed for dark character, a lord, a king or a god of the underworld.

every NPC/follower are friendly

for this mod it has right now two huge dungeon/cave areas and the main home area is under a construction.
I wanted to create some more darker area for the home exterior

NOTE!!! - this is my first released testing mod so if you could give some constructive feedback.
It will contain bugs and not all buildings and stuff are NOT ready yet.

PS. Sorry for my bad english
